The paper is primarily concerned with learning regular languages, which falls under the category of formal languages (cs.FL). The use of a generic model and finite partition of the alphabet suggests a focus on machine learning (cs.LG) and data structures (cs.DS). The implementation of the algorithm and demonstration of its behavior suggest a focus on artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and information theory (cs.IT).
